Personal Injury
Catastrophic injuries or even death can result from an accident such as a slip and fall, auto accident, bicycle/pedestrian accident or negligent security. At Lorenzo & Lorenzo, we are experienced with all types of personal injury cases and the applicable Florida laws.
PERSONAL INJURY
Auto Accident
Car crashes come in many forms. Whether your auto accident was caused by a drunk driver, a hit and run, distracted driving or negligence, the legal team at Lorenzo & Lorenzo are here to help you obtain justice.
AUTO ACCIDENTS
Family Law
Whether it’s divorce, collaborative law, or mediation, we’re here to guide you every step of the way. We understand the emotional toll and commit to making the legal process clear and stress-free for you and your loved ones.
FAMILY LAW
Tractor Trailer Accident
A collision with a semi truck, tractor trailer or 18-wheeler usually results in extensive medical care, chronic injuries, disability or even death. Our truck accident attorneys can help get you the compensation you deserve from insurers and the trucking company.
TRUCK AND TRACTOR TRAILER ACCIDENTS
Motorcycle Accident
Motorcyclists are entitled to the same rights as other drivers. If you are involved in a motorcycle wreck, meet with an expert motorcycle accident attorney at Lorenzo & Lorenzo to talk about your right to compensation.
MOTORCYCLE ACCIDENTS
Immigration
We specialize in family-based immigration, helping families navigate the complex U.S. immigration system with care and expertise. Whether you are petitioning for a spouse, child, parent, or sibling, we provide personalized guidance to ensure your loved ones can reunite and thrive in the United States. Our commitment to family unity drives us to deliver tailored strategies and compassionate advocacy for every client we serve.
IMMIGRATION LAW
