Welcome to
El Toque
We love to make you happy!
This is how our journey began.
With a wealth of culinary expertise gained over the years, we set out on a new adventure in Orlando, pursuing our passion for cooking.
Our journey started on June 1, 2019 when we launched our first venture: The Food Truck. We take pride in offering a delectable array of hot dogs, hamburgers, and other mouthwatering delights from Venezuelan cuisine.
We were thrilled by the positive reception and enthusiastic response from people, which led us to open our first restaurant in Metrowest. This allowed us to broaden our menu and incorporate a variety of creative fusions that showcase the rich flavors of Latin gastronomy, while also incorporating some beloved tastes from our home country, Venezuela.
Currently, we have four locations available for our valued customers to enjoy. Our first location, where our incredible journey began, is still open and thriving as a Food Truck. Additionally, we have a restaurant situated in the vibrant area of Metrowest, another restaurant in the charming town of Casselberry, as well as a recently opened establishment in Davenport.
Come and join us at El Toque to savor the culinary delights we have carefully crafted. We can't wait to have you with us!
Why Us
Why Choose Our Restaurant
Flavor
Our culinary creations tantalize the taste buds with a symphony of flavors, meticulously crafted to delight even the most discerning palate. From bold and savory to delicate and nuanced, each dish is a masterpiece of flavor, showcasing our commitment to culinary excellence.
Service
Service isn't just a duty—it's a passion. Our team of dedicated professionals goes above and beyond to ensure every guest feels welcomed, valued, and attended to with the utmost care. From the moment you enter our doors, expect nothing less than exemplary service.
Cuisine
Embark on a culinary journey with our cuisine. From latin influences and local ingredients, we offer a symphony of flavors and textures to suit every palate. Whether you crave traditional favorites or innovative creations, promising an experience that celebrates the artistry of food.
