Revolutionizing Miami's Dental Experience
Dive into a unique dental experience with Ultra Smile DentalSpa, dentist in Miami, where modern dentistry meets spa-like relaxation. Led by Dr. Bahmadi, a dedicated professional always at the cutting edge of technology, our services range from wisdom teeth extraction to Botox, ensuring you get the best treatments available.
With two conveniently located offices in Midtown, and Miami, we prioritize your satisfaction. Whether you’re enjoying our complimentary yearly whitening or watching your favorite Netflix show during a treatment, our team guarantees an unparalleled experience, like no other dentist in Miami!
OUR MISSION
Our mission is to create a dental spa environment that is ultimately comfortable, modern, safe and clean, where the best quality of care is available to our patients. The care provided will be meticulous, uncompromised and attentive. The care provided will be rendered with the latest technology, state of the art equipment, and with the highest end cosmetic materials and products that will help us in achieving the most beautiful and long lasting results. The care received will be given by a team of professionals that are patient, courteous, friendly, and understanding. Our patients are content and in turn the Ultra Smile team feels the gratification and satisfaction of having served them.
WE ARE PROUDLY FEATURED IN:
WHY CHOOSE ULTRA SMILE?
The latest technology and state of art equipment Dr Bahmadi keeps up to date with the latest technology and state of the art equipment to perform the dentistry her patients deserve. She believes it is important to work with great quality products for long lasting results. She continues educating herself through webinars, podcasts and conferences and is an active member of the ADA, FDA, SFDA, AACD, AAFE.
Ultra Smile is able to provide same day crowns, affordable invisible braces and complimentary whitening once a year to all our patients. Contact us to learn more about our program .
Modern relaxing spa like environment Our Miami Dentist office is a modern and relaxing spa like environment. You will be welcomed with a refreshing drink and snack. During the treatment, you will enjoy the aromatherapy scent chosen exclusively for you to help you relax and breathe better while catching up on your latest TV shows on Netflix, as the doctor is checking and working on you.
To complete the spa experience, you will be handed a scented hot towel to freshen your face and clear off any debris that were splashed. Did you expect to find a dentist in Miami like this?
Dentist in Miami focused on patient satisfaction At our Ultra Smile Miami Dentist Offices, patient’s satisfaction is crucial. Our primary focus will always be YOU. You will be welcomed by a team that is understanding, patient and competent. The doctor will make sure to spend as much time needed to go over the treatment plan with the patient and make sure everything is understood and all possible options are covered.
We thrive to help you with anything you need and offer you insurance prices even if you don’t have any! You can read our reviews to hear what our existing patients have to share about the best dentist in Miami!
