At The Law Office of Daniel J. Fernandez P.A., our top-rated Tampa criminal defense lawyers protect the rights of our clients from the moment the criminal accusation is made to the final resolution of the case. We represent clients across Tampa Bay, including Hillsborough County, Pinellas County, Polk County, Manatee, Sarasota County, Pasco County, Hernando County, and throughout the State of Florida. With decades of experience, including time spent as a former prosecutor, you can rest assured that your case is represented by an attorney who understands the tactics used by the prosecution.
