Tampa Criminal Defense Lawyer – Daniel J. Fernandez, P.A.
When the weight of a criminal charge lands on your shoulders in Hillsborough County, the hours that follow feel heavier than any you have lived before. Bond paperwork, jail visits, worried phone calls from family members, and the quiet dread of wondering what tomorrow looks like all crash together at once. At the law office of Daniel J. Fernandez, P.A., our Tampa criminal defense attorneys have spent more than four decades walking clients through exactly this kind of storm. Located at 625 E Twiggs Street in downtown Tampa, just steps from the Hillsborough County Courthouse, our firm stands ready to answer the call the moment accusation turns into arrest.
Four Decades of Courtroom Battles Across the Bay
Daniel J. Fernandez has been practicing criminal law in Tampa for 43 years, and in that span he has personally tried more than 500 cases to verdict. Those are not settlement numbers or quick pleas. Those are cases where he stood in front of a jury, cross examined witnesses, and argued for the freedom of the man or woman seated beside him at counsel table. That kind of experience is rare in the Tampa Bay legal community, and it is the reason prosecutors know his name before he ever files a notice of appearance.
Before opening his own
Tampa criminal defense
practice, Mr. Fernandez served as a prosecutor, which means he understands the playbook the State Attorney’s Office runs from the other side. He knows how charging decisions get made at the Edgecomb Courthouse, how plea offers are calculated, and how assistant state attorneys prepare for trial. That insider knowledge gets passed directly to every client the firm accepts, whether th",200,Medium,"The firm has over 43 years of experience, a high volume of cases (500+ trials), and 572 Google reviews, indicating a well-established regional presence across Tampa Bay and Florida, though it appears to be centered around a single lead attorney.",Modern,"['Lack of online client portal for secure document sharing and case updates', 'No explicit online scheduling or intake forms mentioned, which could streamline client acquisition', 'Potential for improved CRM integration for lead management given the volume of inquiries']","['Custom Client Portal Development', 'Online Intake Forms & Scheduling Integration', 'CRM Implementation/Optimization', 'Cybersecurity Audit & Data Protection', 'Managed IT Services', 'Advanced SEO/Content Marketing']",8,High,"This established legal firm handles sensitive client data and a high volume of cases, making them an ideal candidate for enhanced cybersecurity, efficient client management systems, and modern client engagement tools like a secure portal.",Legal,"The firm has a strong online presence with a functional, multilingual website and an impressive 572 Google reviews, indicating high visibility and client trust.",False,,2026-07-08 19:15:32.280432
