Dr. Melanie Kucharski-Kalb brings years of dedicated experience in making dental care fun for children. She loves working with kids and enjoys connecting with young patients through engaging conversations and playful interactions, helping each visit feel positive and anxiety-free. Dr. Kalb is committed to creating a warm, comfortable environment where children can build healthy habits and confident smiles.
Melanie Kalb, DMD
Now Offering Orthodontics!
We’re excited to introduce  orthodontic care  with our  board-certified orthodontist , providing  clear braces, metal braces, clear aligners, and more  for children, teens, and adults. Enjoy the convenience of  complete dental and orthodontic care in one place , making every step of your family’s smile journey easier than ever.
