Why Choose Bright Smiles Miami?
Child-Friendly Environment:
Our office features fun activities and interactive displays to keep kids entertained and comfortable
Expert Care:
Our team is highly skilled in working with children, using age-appropriate language and techniques
Convenience & Comfort:
Easy, free parking and a warm greeting from our staff ensure a hassle-free visit for parents and kids alike.
Affordable Membership Plans:
We offer affordable in-house membership plans to make dental care more accessible for your family, helping you save on routine visits and treatments.
We Accept Medicaid:
At Bright Smiles Miami, we believe every child deserves quality dental care. That’s why we proudly accept Medicaid and many other insurance plans, making our services accessible and affordable for all families.
Botox & Fillers for Parents:
While your child is being cared for, you can unwind and indulge in our Botox and dermal filler treatments. Designed to help you look and feel your best, our aesthetic services provide a relaxing experience that allows you to refresh your appearance, all while your child is receiving their dental care.
